title: CT - Computed Tomography
description:
CT - Computed Tomography is an app that was created for all students, radiologists and Graduates in Bio-Image production who wish to learn or reinforce their knowledge in a simple way.

Within the app you will find a human body where you can select different protocols and learn in a didactic and effective way.
In each section of the human body you will find the information necessary to carry out your computed tomography study:

- Indications
- Previous preparation
- Scout view
- Fov
- Cut thickness and gap
- Windows
- Reconstruction plans, etc.

Also in each protocol you find different images.

Wouldn't you like to always have a help for your studies at hand and be able to reinforce your knowledge?

Download CT - Computed Tomography for FREE!
